{"tid":2151884,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"港大新增「文理學士」包括AI Design Fintech Health","createTime":"2020-08-11T15:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T06:01:03.000Z","uid":225931,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3842f33e39317ba0a324df583db425764dd3c081","tid":2151884,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:29:53.000Z","msg":"香港大學將於2019至2020學年開設「文理學士」全新課程。據資料顯示，課程內容包含10個學院參與設計，希望修讀該科目的同學能應付未來15年甚至30年的轉變，並旨在培養未來社會領袖。<br />\n<br />\n文理學士共有五個學士學位課程，預計共招收約100人。五個學士學位課程包括：<br />\n1）文理學士【BASc】<br />\n2）文理學士(應用人工智能)【BASc(Applied AI)】<br />\n3）文理學士(設計+)【BASc(Design+)】<br />\n4）文理學士(金融科技)【BASc(FinTech)】<br />\n5）文理學士(環球衞生及發展) 【BASc(GHD)】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上述系列學士課程共涉及10個學院，有利課程將文學與科學結合，培育學生綜合不同知識領域的思考方法，而部份課程會由兩名不同學系的教授授課，可讓學生更能掌握不同學科之間的關連。<br />\n<br />\n此外，校方會要求學生前往國外頂尖學府交流，如耶魯大學、倫郭大學學院及加州柏克萊大學等，他們亦會透過課程到機構實習，包括聯合國（UN）、世界衛生組織（WHO）和谷歌（Google）等，讓同學可與不同背景的團隊合作從中學習。"},{"pid":"e6be1a698a2464d10dd9e02f20854322682b6687","tid":2151884,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3c21f086a1813f26eeaeaaf07d1c9514f7d86a","tid":2151884,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:31:58.000Z","msg":"Design+<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee33257154e5b4779b56900872d719803c4a9e93","tid":2151884,"uid":8441,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:35:15.000Z","msg":"仲有得去美帝交流 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afd7e426c80fd47e9907d06ad6b